====File→Output As action====

This action will pop up an ~KOutput As~E save file chooser dialog
through which you can choose the folder, filename, and extension to
output your index into. If the file already exists, you will be asked if
you want to replace it.

To invoke, use ~K__F__ile→Ou__t__put As~E.

If the ~F.docx~E file already exists, you will be asked if you want to
replace it.

~WIf the output file is //open// in another application (e.g., a
word-processor), you must close it before using this action
[(Note) xix_file_footnote.html].~E

